He had no sense of color coordination.

324
00:26:55,356 --> 00:26:58,943
Although l hardly remember him.
l didn't have time to socialize.

325
00:26:59,569 --> 00:27:01,696
I was far too busy with my...

326
00:27:02,405 --> 00:27:03,489
...studies.

327
