Now, class, is everyone almost finished?

328
00:27:08,953 --> 00:27:10,830
And if the truth be told, he....

329
00:27:11,164 --> 00:27:12,248
He liked Martha.

330
00:27:14,167 --> 00:27:16,044
Martha was my girlfriend.

331
