Aaron B. Benson Who, l hate you.

389
00:32:50,420 --> 00:32:52,547
Hate, hate, hate.
Hate, hate, hate.

390
00:32:52,630 --> 00:32:54,090
Double hate.

391
00:32:54,716 --> 00:32:58,136
Loathe entirely!

392
00:33:05,018 --> 00:33:06,811
Nutcrackers?

393
00:33:07,604 --> 00:33:10,481
lt's their Whobilation.

394
