00:37:30,450 --> 00:37:32,327
Must drown them out!

464
00:37:41,878 --> 00:37:43,755
Not working!

465
00:37:45,506 --> 00:37:48,927
The whipperwinds whipped
high above the Who town.

466
00:37:49,052 --> 00:37:52,722
A trip or a slip
you'd slide all the way down.

467
00:37:53,431 --> 00:37:56,684
But this girl had a mission.
She knew what to do.

468
00:37:56,768 --> 00:38:01,147
She'd invite the Grinch herself,
that brave Cindy Lou.

469
00:38:09,530 --> 00:38:12,700
Play, monkey! Play!

470
00:38:25,046 --> 00:38:26,839
Howdy?

471
00:38:30,134 --> 00:38:31,719
Mr. Grinch?

472
00:38:34,764 --> 00:38:36,641
Mr. Grinch!

473
00:38:41,396 --> 00:38:42,564
Hello?

474
00:39:08,882 --> 00:39:10,258
Excuse me.

475
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:27,650
Hello...

476
00:39:28,151 --> 00:39:29,611
...little girl.

477
00:39:30,111 --> 00:39:32,655
How dare you enter...

478
00:39:32,947 --> 00:39:35,408
...the Grinch's lair?

479
00:39:35,533 --> 00:39:38,494
The impudence! The audacity!

480
00:39:38,995 --> 00:39:41,456
The unmitigated gall!

481
00:39:41,539 --> 00:39:43,583
You called down the thunder...

482
00:39:43,708 --> 00:39:47,128
...now, get ready for the boom!

483
00:39:48,004 --> 00:39:51,925
Gaze into the face of fear!

484
00:39:54,344 --> 00:39:55,845
Mr. Grinch...

485
00:39:56,721 --> 00:39:58,681
...my name is Cindy Lou Who.

486
00:39:58,765 --> 00:39:59,766
You see?

487
00:39:59,891 --> 00:40:04,187
Even now the terror
is welling up inside you.

488
00:40:05,438 --> 00:40:07,023
l'm not scared.

489
00:40:07,232 --> 00:40:11,361
Denial is to be expected
in the face of pure evil.

490
00:40:13,529 --> 00:40:15,114
l don't think so.

491
00:40:16,241 --> 00:40:17,408
Doubt?

492
00:40:17,492 --> 00:40:21,329
Another unmistakable sign
of the heebie-jeebies!

493
00:40:22,038 --> 00:40:25,542
Now you're doomed!

494
00:40:33,174 --> 00:40:35,134
Run for your life...

495
00:40:35,218 --> 00:40:38,638
...before l kill again!

496
00:40:41,140 --> 00:40:42,684
l'm a psycho!

497
00:40:45,687 --> 00:40:48,064
Danger! Danger!

498
00:40:57,282 --> 00:40:59,409
Maybe you need a time-out.

499
00:41:05,039 --> 00:41:06,291
Kids today.

500
00:41:06,416 --> 00:41:09,335
So desensitized by movies and television.

501
00:41:10,128 --> 00:41:11,462
What do you want?

502
00:41:12,755 --> 00:41:15,758
Mr. Grinch, l came to invite you...

503
00:41:16,593 --> 00:41:18,970
...to be holiday cheermeister.

504
00:41:21,431 --> 00:41:24,517
-''Holiday Whobie-what-y''?
-Cheermeister.

505
00:41:25,602 --> 00:41:27,896
''Cheermeister. Celebrate with friends.''

506
00:41:32,233 --> 00:41:33,735
That's a good one.

507
00:41:34,527 --> 00:41:38,531
l know you hate Christmas,
but what if it's all just a misunderstanding?

508
00:41:38,698 --> 00:41:42,368
-Don't care.
-l myself am having some Yuletide doubts.

509
00:41:43,036 --> 00:41:46,539
But maybe if you reunite
with the Whos and be a part of Christmas--

510
00:41:46,623 --> 00:41:49,626
''Maybe if you reunite with the Whos
and be a part of Christmas.''

511
00:41:49,709 --> 00:41:50,710
Grow up!

512
00:41:50,835 --> 00:41:52,879
Then maybe it'll be all right for me, too!

513
00:41:52,962 --> 00:41:54,464
l'm sorry, your session is over.

514
00:41:54,547 --> 00:41:57,717
Please make another appointment
with the receptionist on the way out.

515
00:41:57,800 --> 00:42:00,178
Please, please.
You have to accept the award.

516
00:42:05,725 --> 00:42:07,435
Award?

517
00:42:09,854 --> 00:42:12,941
